title: MBMBaM 406: Face 2 Face: Sweet Dreams, Timothy
description: Travis is on vacation this week, so we're happy to present to you our live show in gorgeous Columbus, Ohio from our most recent tour! It's got thrills, chills and spills, and also a new method for handling audience questions that resulted in some REAL humdingers.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
